Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.95,0:00:05.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,0)}南非地區  礦物資源採掘現場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.30,0:00:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  慘不忍睹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.64,0:00:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.43,0:00:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不在這進行石塊的採掘  那這個國家的經濟就崩潰了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受此影響的國家和企業到底會有多少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.13,0:00:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像只管阻止戰爭  而不管老百姓如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長  PMC托拉斯來電
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阿里·阿爾·沙謝斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.39,0:00:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  派遣我們來到現場卻又要取消  什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.50,0:00:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雇傭軍就是要來戰鬥的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.71,0:00:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若這樣下去  那莫拉里亞會瓦解的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.37,0:00:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  我們回本部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.14,0:00:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.05,0:00:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算可以實現了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.20,0:00:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AEU的大人物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.57,0:00:53.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,250)}AEU中央議會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.59,0:00:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都要向莫拉里亞派遣軍隊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.66,0:00:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙開發計劃中需要莫拉里亞的PMC
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.56,0:01:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這在前些天的歐洲首腦會議上也確認過了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.02,0:01:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  就算莫拉里亞的經濟在逐漸走向崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.73,0:01:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果擁護莫拉里亞  那Celestial Being會…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.63,0:01:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才要派遣軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.74,0:01:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若將我國的士兵派遣到國外  那會引起人們的反對…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.67,0:01:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起擔心3個世紀前的事來  目前更應該考慮AEU的利益
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.26,0:01:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殖民地開發的話  交給聯合和人革聯不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.73,0:01:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若沒有我方的資金  那他們就沒法作為
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.04,0:01:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,資金雄厚的貴國說不定是可以辦到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.85,0:01:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但本國的情況就…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們國家就那麼想出售自己的武器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不增強軍備  那進軍宇宙什麼的就是空話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.59,0:01:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若宇宙開發也被聯合和人革聯控制
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.56,0:01:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們會失去最後的前線陣地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.69,0:01:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.64,0:02:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙開發競爭中我們不能再落後了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就僅由贊成國家向莫拉里亞派遣軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.24,0:02:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  此次派遣軍隊將視為AEU的全體意見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要成為拯救莫拉里亞的白馬騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:57.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,0)}#06  七劍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN驅動器  連接良好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:04:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子的充填狀況  目前為75%
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散佈狀況固定在40%
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可視區域內沒有未知物體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  都過了一週多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是指阿里路亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好啊  救人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這頭疼是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我不用繼續單獨待著了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.48,0:04:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是  不過你完全沒反省呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亞·哈普提茲姆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你並不適合當Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想把我趕下Kyrios嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.38,0:04:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我是想這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.47,0:04:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不能這麼辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:05:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又需要你的幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫拉里亞共和國的總統\N和AEU主要參與國的外相進行了秘密會談
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得到了以上消息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫拉里亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是PMC吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可以看作是對我們的挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是項艱巨的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也會到地面上進行協助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除阿里路亞的禁閉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩位  請馬上進行出擊準備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:34.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,250)}人革聯  低軌道平台
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然對少尉的身體進行了徹底檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但沒發現什麼問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦內的神經反應正常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.07,0:05:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神經膠質細胞也顯示正常數值
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:40.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,250)}超人機關技術研究所  分所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  少尉為何會做出那種行動？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在分析了桃子的任務記錄器之後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們檢測到在少尉的腦量子波中存在異常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.67,0:05:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一般是不可能的現象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.61,0:06:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是受到了來自外部的影響…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外部的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.87,0:06:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那施加影響的人只能是與少尉一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神經膠質細胞進行了強化  使用腦量子波的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是說是同類嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想表明可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對應措施呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在少尉的制服裡設置了遮斷腦量子波的裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會重蹈覆轍的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼想讓少尉上戰場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不出現Celestial Being等組織
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們的研究也就不會公諸於眾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想以此為由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:40.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}AEU  法國首都
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是太陽光發電的技術支援嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:45.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,250)}法國  外交部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懇請助一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我國也很想幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但貴國的形勢極不穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若無法確保我國所派遣技術人員的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:07:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那估計議會也不會同意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便不是這樣  AEU的軌道電梯並未完全運作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.94,0:07:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不知道有沒有餘力外派技術人員…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.54,0:07:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.52,0:07:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會盡力繼續對阿扎提斯坦進行糧食援助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年輕的公主想頂著無法適應的外交來保護國家嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很可憐  但我們也沒有餘力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也只能靠莫拉里亞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  正好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是煮雞肉  姐姐做得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.13,0:07:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話  要不嘗嘗…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正要出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是場災難
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是說在平台…  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:08:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然會被Celestial Being救了一命  真沒想到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.47,0:08:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫拉里亞共和國
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在23年前的2284年建國
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個位於歐洲南部的小國
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.02,0:08:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人口只有很少的18萬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在國內卻有著300萬以上的外國勞動人員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約4000個民企的兩成是PMC
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.71,0:08:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂PMC  即以業務來承包雇傭兵的派遣  士兵的培養
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兵器運輸  以及兵器開發  軍隊維持的民間軍事企業
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真有熱心啊  菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是任務啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.39,0:08:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.72,0:08:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫拉里亞是通過優待吸引來的民間軍事企業進行發展的國家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.62,0:08:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼之前都沒有成為我們的攻擊對象呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若世界的戰爭減少  那他們就會失去業務
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.84,0:09:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若就這樣自生自滅就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫拉里亞好像打算和Celestial Being對著來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有AEU做後盾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.24,0:09:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了完成太陽光發電系統  而進軍殖民地開發
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民間軍事企業的人才和技術不可或缺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是莫拉里亞  也想重整縮水的經濟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算自己國家成為戰場  也需要AEU的援助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  若是配合的好  估計還想把Gundam弄到手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.07,0:09:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  那樣的話  這次好像只好讓給他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AEU的王牌們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是莫拉里亞空軍基地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.39,0:09:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,允許降落  請使用7號跑道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.48,0:09:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  我是AEU的王牌——帕特里克·克拉薩烏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來助你們一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫拉里亞空軍的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.94,0:10:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點來吧  Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要好好整整你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.69,0:10:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫拉里亞和AEU的共同軍事演習？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是聯隊規模的派遣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.21,0:10:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外  莫拉里亞的民間軍事企業的軍事聯合鬥爭組織
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PMC托拉斯也參加演習
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若將他們的MS加在一起  要超過130台
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大規模的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界將不得不矚目Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐  直飛莫拉里亞是在明天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.87,0:10:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前可以自由行動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.31,0:10:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想那麼做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:10:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話  行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.28,0:11:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特  去購物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.02,0:11:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務計劃的論證還沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們越是活躍  物價就會越高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以必須趁現在預先把想買的買好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數據分析…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.43,0:11:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  皇小姐  我們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,論證…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  去喝點東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.89,0:11:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好久不見  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.12,0:11:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩·巴斯蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有樣東西想儘早交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.98,0:11:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是樣有意思的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮物  禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames的附加武器先安裝上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.09,0:11:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你的是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia專用GN刀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與GN劍一樣  釋放高壓縮粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以輕鬆地切斷厚度3米的E-Carbon
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.22,0:12:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  感動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.02,0:12:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN刀…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam  七劍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.65,0:12:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算有點像Exia的開發代號了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.05,0:12:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是十萬火急地把它運到這種小島上的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也感謝一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很感謝了  那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.10,0:12:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那的腦袋裡只有Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  我的Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:04.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,250)}聯合領域內  某旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:04.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到中午了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JNN今日新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的特輯是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.79,0:13:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對在莫拉里亞共和國進行的與AEU的聯合軍事演習
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,——Operation Dawn的核實
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此次雙方總共投入了100台以上MS演習
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但為何會在這種時期大規模地…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.98,0:13:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.93,0:13:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Une Puree
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是你的話  認為莫拉里亞的動向會是如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣啦  難得和你見面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自研究生院以來  已經有幾年不見了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼說嘛  會暴露我的年紀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.25,0:13:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈  早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.32,0:13:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女的要是被說出實際年齡  那青春會相應地折損哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種實證資料怎麼會有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.43,0:14:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是老樣子呢  比利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.75,0:14:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能邀請我  我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好滿足啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.77,0:14:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.55,0:14:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對Gundam調查隊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼名稱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.80,0:14:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是剛剛新設立的  正式名稱還沒確定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你屬於那個部隊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.91,0:14:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光是我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.54,0:14:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,技術主任可是艾夫曼教授哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授已經注意到了Gundam釋放出的特殊粒子的概念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  是什麼粒子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我很想問出個究竟  但都沒回答我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不管這事  你現在在忙什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.94,0:14:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  胡亂忙活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.56,0:14:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.22,0:15:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.66,0:15:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.14,0:15:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能這樣再次相遇  我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這件也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.16,0:15:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  好可愛～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.73,0:15:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我睡會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出所料  果然只是得到了糧食援助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說的好像理所當然嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想辦法確保技術支援的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你從新聞裡也得知了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫拉里亞將與Celestial Being發生紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若戰局長久持續  那您得回來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡  Celestial Being也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合演習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到AEU會參加啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是外交努力的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.29,0:15:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若只有我們的話  那不會採取這種不合理的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:16:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要讓AEU也嘗嘗苦頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.49,0:16:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:08.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(250,250)}PMC  武器倉庫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.34,0:16:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把這台機體交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AEU的新型號嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是開發實驗用的機體  在我公司的技術部門進行了調整
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這傢伙能擊倒Gundam？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.19,0:16:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是捕獲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得輕巧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是給你準備了夠吃喝一輩子的賞金哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙  相當有魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.75,0:16:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭候多時了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我來帶路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是王留美  安排得很出色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敢當
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.39,0:16:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…莫拉里亞和AEU軍的配備狀況吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有PMC托拉斯  而且是實時的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候侵入的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.49,0:17:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早飯之前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如預定  在00點開始任務
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標是消除所有與我們敵對的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  是和九條啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.82,0:17:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九條…莫非是那次事件的戰況預報員？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現場來的影像到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.96,0:17:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯示在顯示屏上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.77,0:17:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,資料中可沒有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being  是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目視確認了Gundam  地點是A4576
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方好像注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.19,0:17:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各機  遵照任務計劃展開行動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將密碼線路常開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐會傳來變更的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:17:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫拉里亞宣佈遭遇緊急事態
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快報  準備字幕機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.87,0:18:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快製作緊急特別節目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫拉里亞共和國宣佈遭遇緊急事態
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.06,0:18:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是說Celestial Being已經開始了武力干預…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.23,0:18:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在打仗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.40,0:18:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam出現了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.54,0:18:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太奇怪了  路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being明明拯救了我們  卻又展開了戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.70,0:18:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此  世界也不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.39,0:18:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只會導致憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.73,0:18:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們只是在擾亂世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李本茲  我好像聽到了…世界的惡意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.51,0:18:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在E332捕捉到敵方飛行部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐的預測真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:18:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:18:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲不開！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.38,0:19:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊破敵機編隊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios  任務計劃無變動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  繼續干預行動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.49,0:19:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames  Virtue  轉移至D883進行武力干預
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.23,0:19:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅  護盾控制  拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.75,0:19:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧  交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.95,0:19:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  根本不用狙擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.17,0:19:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這  這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.68,0:19:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意後方  注意後方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷襲  正好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue  一次掃清Hellion部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:19:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.65,0:20:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然和上次的型號不同  但你也應該是Gundam吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就一定是我的敵人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.34,0:20:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人MS從G653快速靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.78,0:20:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  將目標全部殲滅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務…繼續進行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.32,0:20:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue已完成第一階段  進入了第二階段
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios壓制了敵空中兵力  突入第二階段
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將Dynames的任務計劃改為C5
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是Gundam Meister的能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.62,0:20:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不止如此  這才剛剛開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia狀況如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.05,0:20:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和預定的一樣  正在T554和敵方部隊交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  第一階段結束  轉為第二階段
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.44,0:21:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型號？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.87,0:21:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.52,0:21:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作被看穿了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.97,0:21:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是機體再好  機師不行的話還是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  Gundam啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個聲音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡來妨礙生意！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不會是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊可搭著獎金呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:21:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.89,0:22:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歸我了  Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.24,0:23:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人因義而行動  亦因利而行動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.76,0:23:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬間的勝利  蘊含著絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.17,0:23:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  「沒有回報的靈魂」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.72,0:23:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷疑著Gundam的真正價值


